config ZMK_HUD
    bool "ZMK HUD Broadcaster"
    default n
    depends on RAW_HID
    help
      Broadcasts layer state and key press events via Raw HID
      for use with desktop HUD applications.

      When enabled, the keyboard will send HID reports containing:
      - Layer activation/deactivation events
      - Key press/release events with position and modifier state

      Requires the zmk-raw-hid module to be enabled.
